I agree with what Greg said, Keep the head temp below
450, also I found out that the oil temp is very
important too, keep it below 230F or you stand a good
chance of gauling the P/L's. the oil temp can exceed
limits with the head temp below 450F, so you have to
keep a eye on both of them. Phil


